 on improving test coverage for the active class's `doCall` instead.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0a589b4568d13dbb016a2737966e2881909abe7ec1d622921f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJze8nHIoGCI8KJlllvw6VSsWD6EFfcJV7EM370OYqPDHPk2hLVbnUD0g58rK0QOl5BNam8fShs8QpQm1RYMZVx6bD6b_vWpxpO-CjNCS4612bSNF9rmtz8TLwKYcpmdjZ6itcY9fzSejBq9yQP_ybvVxv0eTucugPHsdsQBxPDqVyrW2eincUIU-AjkOe0P4QnHKaa44rplpU7a6Zw_pOfZSd92UuNUSu6A4WSArn0Y4dJTqWbh8PjWSITfDlpvuM_QwAZS6WQfLKhT_IDHOS2ir4L3p8mygyKjuhY8fZsuPW5pJxWZAK1uexhrVBRPcmi1Oc8TE9F6irY2U05puaTsDnaN_-AWxYXc2lXur20Bv666vK7YxFbAQKUqICY443-2exqOlmcK2Wf5z1hgLexJ-fjA92jDHeRqJ6bsJqkRJ6DGfTMZJxho0wo61MySFWahWdiD9x96OGFD8agrzJv0cftbH6wxY57J9jQeuxItLYJXqEyObkDejCXd2DIY1AB_C-bsPnWYyx_jpnUmDj7c1d49Q7J9A8RjUvvM_bAidIMGVSlr1gytvqnQLW_iZLOEg2RomnHIv7Z2_zjvAUF2IRRFzgDl1UkwBtJYkmYrNHyXnqEHXv6t6OmoD2LMH2Yp4i7LgmTjiICvPPRcqQK6moVMawxOSaTI9ZZN7OShF6KZ9F6B9YJ-hLzd2FrzengYZUYPxMW-JVfRQUkMAFy_oYboiYEeCfSIX3GNPxRQZLotNjKbv89UvYHMR29BPy5Ly5bms4zxs3ws3wHxpMW7qNzOZv5wXKRFMkDpwPGD6gFJWuGlq-LAhy-vV5ukaf9pIJHNR4qLMz2MPWiYUvyIf68FxiJbJYm7S0IL99w33FyZ59I5yebfy1YDLxf0jIsCqO_hWvPvnHz7l61mylFsOo7wzWs6CtjIgpont6_uK_lMPICcG9cLa_9M6RGPTtFIvvfynU4mBHNoTz8aT6pxD7E3YklZwIel5FFVc2lknVGC7HdwWJi6ZnfZXQTtgxylOWRctbm3DaMx_QsVqct_JVZdcoD5ETWBfxlXmji3mDY1qrDuZbUqB0oFoLtKc5G4jrcOH4vjv7fa7E5vEVzF46NzdJ0HpDdXAhpjK9tXS4QODlNKIs7Ao2qQ2rHBazxk7TECZu2DdbCx6bNEN2KAQ030-V6g_Knv4Eaj1anzWViVz-zH-u4tf2p49VwAdPBrpoan4fECi7lbBmRvLmROgQKJbnnN2ASpGdwbJ4YWsTNURchG6V8uk1-uFAut9nNBYZ67gVy2jlK3Lmxz9ablZlyZX76TiMpbLgNUFSKew74qcNZfUG_CNsY6QhBCaXDD7QdnD5Tb-CVTXftdqoEfrMVNoFHJ-ANtCjX1SyV4Ky7xP45XqzAGW_gztW3wc_HpAvgTNjCKbuNSkdR_Delyyugww6xEaLshPBL2ZrXIW91FH_RLYWouHRWp_MT3yYLc0wcb6aM8ZtK86OblOlV3Z9356vY8ySr4iYzulCATODazsmNYcmBVI5zBhstlTVreVrhfmQr9RXmTarjJ1O6e1U8-8mQ5VMycQSF_I2KrzR574p21kK5Fc3x4dsw1QSMuiMbVMc3VbxCud3m_v1PXnLl70YqPGjgvK_HwuIPLPkBpoAmd6Djpsv3NJ9jXREYXOYUqXEFyqgJHap_mtts2WrW-Q4PWDAsLNhJEEshPNjE68GkUjIi-_0TUpRl0aBo3fF7kBLXC4L4tYNOeUdTkTBZZRxeCzeqYudC0EOEU